    <item>
      <title>阿拉比卡咖啡价格跌至近两年高点，烘焙商调涨价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/arabica-coffee-holds-near-two-year-high-risking-pricier-lattes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于供应担忧加剧，阿拉比卡咖啡期货价格在迅速上涨至两年来最高水平后开始降温，有可能推高消费者咖啡因摄入成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/arabica-coffee-holds-near-two-year-high-risking-pricier-lattes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:39:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
